name: Socially Awkward
description:
On 03/30/2019 I created this musical piece, with acoustic guitar, bass, keyboard, E-drums and my voice :)
I had just recovered from being homeless for a couple years, as well as from a reasonably toxic relationship. Thus, this song is inspired by my nostalgic home-town strolls and my flustering snapchat conversations with suburban girls. Thank you for enjoying! Much love
